澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 赵实2月22日下午，湖北省新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情防控工作指挥部召开新闻发布会，介绍全省疫情防控医疗物资和生活物资保障情况。
Pai journalist Zhao Shi Feb 22 afternoon, Hubei Province, the new-style coronavirus pneumonia command held a press conference to introduce the province's epidemic prevention and control of medical supplies and supplies.
发布会上，有记者提问，近期有武汉市民反映，婴儿配方奶粉不好买，超市也出现了婴儿配方奶粉缺货的现象。
At the press conference, a reporter asked, Wuhan city recently reported that infant formula is not easy to buy, supermarkets also have a shortage of infant formula.
如何保障婴幼儿奶粉的供应？湖北省商务厅厅长秦军表示，婴幼儿奶粉是一种非常特殊的产品，虽然很小众，但非常重要，而且具有不可替代性。
How to ensure the supply of infant milk powder? Qin Jun, director of the commerce department in Hubei Province, said that infant milk powder was a very special product.
目前湖北省婴幼儿奶粉保有量是1600吨，可以满足全省婴幼儿饮用的时间是一个月以上。
At present, the amount of infant milk powder in Hubei Province is 1,600 tons, can meet the province's infant drinking time is more than one month.
秦军介绍，湖北省婴幼儿奶粉的销售方式主要有两种，70%的销售通过专营店销售，还有30%通过超市销售。
Qin said there were two main sales methods for baby milk powder in Hubei province, 70 percent of which were sold through specialty stores and 30 percent through supermarkets.
“前一段时间因为防疫需求，各家专营店没有营业，所以导致结构性的短缺，发现问题以后，湖北省商务厅与湖北的7家大经销商进行沟通，将原来以专营店销售的方式，转变为超市销售的方式，并且加大了线上销售的力度，目前这个问题基本得到缓解。
"Some time ago, due to the epidemic prevention needs, the specialized shops did not open, which led to structural shortages. After the discovery of the problem, the Hubei Business Office communicated with seven major dealers in Hubei Province.
”本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
Xing Tam, editor of this issue, recommends reading.
